{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f0d4c2e0c9","title":"请求辞去“总书记”职务","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8f1103a3f6","index":0,"year":1924,"month":8,"day":19,"articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","name":"斯大林选集（诸夏怀斯社2017年5月）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"斯大林，诸夏怀斯社2017年5月","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1332d101b8","name":"斯大林"}]},"publication_details":{"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e5e941c20f","type":"paragraph","text":"请求辞去“总书记”职务","index":0,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"b8b5cf163a","type":"paragraph","text":"一一致俄共（布）中央全会的信","index":1,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"84d4363cb5","type":"paragraph","text":"（1924年8月19日）俄共中央全会：","index":2,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"5947c02f71","type":"paragraph","text":"从列宁离职到以后进世，我与季诺维也夫和加米浑夫同志在政治局共事已经一年半了，这段经历使我清整地意识到，我不可能在一个小的集体范围内，与这两位同志开诚布公地共同进行政治工作。有鉴于此，我请求批准我退出中央政治局。","index":3,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"caaf367a99","type":"paragraph","text":"鉴于总书记不可能不是政治局委员，也请求我退出中央书记处（和组织局）。","index":4,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"d0db20d4bd","type":"paragraph","text":"请批准我休假进行治疗，为期约两个月。","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"0503dd9905","type":"paragraph","text":"休假期满后，我请求另行分配工作，或者到图鲁汉斯克边疆区，或者到雅库特州，或者到国外的任何地方，从事不显眼的工作。","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"fc368e5f02","type":"paragraph","text":"上述问题，请全会在我缺席和我不作任何说明的情况下加以解决，因为我认为，除了这封信的第一段已提出的意见外，再作其他说明都于事业不利。","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"f56c16ae96","type":"paragraph","text":"悬请古比雪夫同志将这封信的副本分送给各位中央委员。","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"df6bb4e51f","type":"paragraph","text":"致以共产主义的敬礼！","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"8f46380ca3","type":"paragraph","text":"约·斯天林","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"184a42790e","type":"paragraph","text":"1924年8月19日古比雪天同志：","index":11,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"f87160c028","type":"paragraph","text":"我写此信给您，而不是给中央书记们，是因为：第一，在这件可谓有争执的事情中，我不可能绕过中央监察委员会：第二，中央书记们不了解此事的有关情况，我也不愿平白地打抚他们。","index":12,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"f9efeb066d","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林原载俄罗斯《祖国》杂志","index":13,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"cb6ee1d02f","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集","index":14,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"},{"id":"bd77c818d2","type":"paragraph","text":"档案附卷一第165—166页1994年第7期","index":15,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9"}],"page":{"id":"646210f8db","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"f0d4c2e0c9","start":2498,"end":2499}}}},"__N_SSG":true}